(65, 1, '2017-03-27 20:56:25', '2017-03-27 20:56:25', '<p class="vc_custom_heading section-title"><strong>Why Visit Gyumri? </strong>Because Gyumri is unique and you can not miss it. The most indigenious architecture preserved from 19th century is here to take you to a historical trip of Alexandrapol, one of the most splendid towns of its time. You will have a real cultural experience visiting museums and galleries that tell the story of the city, its talents and its lifestyle. The churches, memorials, monuments, streets, and even the water fountains all bear legends to be discovered by you in the ancient town of Gyumri. And most importantly, you will meet Gyumretsis, honest and humourous people that have preserved national traditions and values from their ancestors, but at the same time have developed their unique characteristics to amaze you at every step.</p>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-27 20:56:25', '2017-03-27 20:56:25', '', 4, 'http://localhost:8080/finish%20work/index.php/2017/03/27/4-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
