(105, 1, '2017-03-28 19:22:26', '2017-03-28 19:22:26', 'A woman gave birth to triplets in the Austrian Children''s Hospital in Gyumri, Armenia''s second largest city.\r\n\r\nA 30-year-old woman, who was could get pregnant for six years, gave birth to two baby girls and a boy, head of medical center Ashot Kurginyan told <a href="https://news.am/eng/" target="_blank">Armenian News-NEWS.am</a>. The woman got pregnant with the help of IVF.\r\n\r\nThe doctors describe the condition of mother and the newborn babies as “satisfactory”.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Gyumri woman gives birth to triplets', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '35-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-28 19:22:26', '2017-03-28 19:22:26', '', 35, 'http://localhost:8080/finish%20work/?p=105', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
